P3 endopod ♂ : not sexually dimorphic. P5 with outer basal seta and between one and three discrete elements; innermost element fused to segment forming spinous process (weakly delimited in
Neoleptastacus trisetosus
); length of process sometimes sexually dimorphic. P 6 ♂ with one or two seta(e).
